title: Anthony Husbands
text:
Anthony Husbands (born January 13, 1956 on <a href="Trinidad">Trinidad</a>) is a retired sprinter from <a href="Trinidad%20and%20Tobago">Trinidad and Tobago</a> who specialized in the <a href="200%20metres">200 metres</a>.
He attended the <a href="Essex%20Community%20College">Essex Community College</a>, Maryland, USA.
